# Troubleshooting Guide

## 1. Lambda "AccessDenied" Errors
**Symptom**:
```
An error occurred (AccessDeniedException) when calling PutItem operation
```

**Fix**:
```bash
aws iam attach-role-policy \
    --role-name lambda-kinesis-role \
    --policy-arn arn:aws:iam::aws:policy/AmazonDynamoDBFullAccess
```

## 2. Kinesis Data Not Reaching Lambda
**Checklist**:
- Verify Kinesis stream and Lambda are in same region
- Confirm IAM role has `kinesis:GetRecords` permission
- Check stream metrics in AWS Console for incoming data

## 3. High Latency
**Solutions**:
- Increase Lambda timeout (default is 3 sec)
- Reduce batch size in Kinesis trigger